:"<blockquote><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20170926/s00007/4741c522ca661f4aa05fae4a2d3a847d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20170926%2Fs00007%2F4741c522ca661f4aa05fae4a2d3a847d.jpg&h=49cf567f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事主向本報提供聲稱是經紀手寫的還款計劃，列明事主第6年可轉銀行，每月只需償還低於2萬元貸款。（受訪者提供）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170926/s00002/1506364580616\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170926%2Fs00002%2F1506364580616&d=Iq2FboJiTy84OGc%2Be90xiUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=0d654011\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170926%2Fs00002%2F1506364580616&h=3fa8379f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170926/s00002/1506364580616</a></blockquote><br />\n地產狗寫隻字都寫到乞兒咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8c734f91a2b774e3ae269415aaad3276ffae83","tid":416307,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:50:34.000Z","msg":"不過人地有父幹母幹 到最尾應該都唔使撻既"},{"pid":"9f046da9d96aa3f67b2770897c6d604be6cceec7","tid":416307,"uid":36995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:51:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實月入5萬，想買800幾萬既樓，真係傻撚左</blockquote><br />\n兩個人夾埋先得5萬<br />\n首期問老豆老母借<br />\n<br />\n一有咩冬瓜豆腐<br />\n俾人炒撚左 或者收入減少<br />\n害鳩埋自己老母老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccaba62911293079465905c84ad7bd3f64da0514","tid":416307,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:54:13.000Z","msg":"月入加埋得五萬學人買800萬層樓，驗腦啦傻閪"},{"pid":"f1bcf0d919448d5340decc1053613f53264380c5","tid":416307,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:00:51.000Z","msg":"呼吸plan簡直用自己人生去賭<br />\n總要累父母"},{"pid":"a5a1a008e773786f5988b8b7bc1de93019378b84